posting_body: ['*** PRIME MID-WILSHIRE LOCATION!', "TWO MILES FROM THE HISTORIC GROVE AT FARMERS MARKET, THE MELROSE AVENUE SHOPPING DISTRICT, AND THE BEVERLY CENTER, LA'S PREMIER FOOD, FASHION, AND SHOPPING DESTINATION.", '***', 'Your Villa Vicente key opens more than the door to your home.', 'It uncovers a tropical paradise.', 'Escape to a four-acre residential resort surrounded by the calming sounds of fountains and gentle streams.', 'Our community of apartment homes features well-appointed units in a beautiful tropical courtyard setting.', 'This gated community is professionally managed with excellent management and maintenance staff.', 'Ideally located near a plethora of shopping, dining and entertainment options, our Los Angeles rental homes offer air conditioning, mirrored closets, and balconies or patios in most units.', 'Visit our residential community and discover tranquil living and big city convenience.', '- Minutes to Larchmont Village, The Grove, The Beverly Center and Melrose Avenue Dinning and Shopping', '- Private patio or balcony', '- Minutes to La Brea Tarpits, LACMA, and Petersen Automotive Museum', '- Mirrored oversized closets', '- Studio and one-bedroom layouts', '- Refrigerator & microwave', '- Minutes to Wilshire La Brea Dog Relief Park and Hancock Park', '- 24-hour emergency on-call maintenance', '- Hardwood-style flooring', '- Nightly courtesy patrol', '- Internet café', '- Air conditioning', 'Call:', 'show contact info', 'For more information, visit us at: <URL>', 'Pricing is subject to change.', 'Call for details.']
